\f2\b0 \cf0 Mac OS X can also run X-windows applications using free third party software. These applications run side by side with regular Mac OS X programs. Fink is a system which can download and compile these applications on Mac OS X. For details, see http://fink.sourceforge.net. In particular, Fink can install ghostview, xdvi, and xemacs.\
